      "updated": 1782066368277,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 22.05360969484466,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "text": "A browser app that shows HOW your documents\nreference each other, step by step.\n\nDrag in .docx / .pdf / .md / .txt / .json and it pulls\nthe text in memory, then draws a directed graph of\nhow each document cites the others.\n\nGoal: make citations, audit trails & file integrity\nVISIBLE instead of buried across scattered specs.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A browser app that shows HOW your documents\nreference each other, step by step.\n\nDrag in .docx / .pdf / .md / .txt / .json and it pulls\nthe text in memory, then draws a directed graph of\nhow each document cites the others.\n\nGoal: make citations, audit trails & file integrity\nVISIBLE instead of buried across scattered specs.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 13,
      "index": "a5",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r-7",
      "x": 1051.2907717081337,
      "y": -3.4613567247690753,
      "width": 1065.347276612504,
      "height": 510.534113708337,
