      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 24.347987561732214,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "text": "- Built with Vite + React (npm install once).\n- LANDING -> ENTER WORKSPACE / SCAN / EXPORT.\n- SCAN: drag a .docx/.pdf/.md/.txt/.json file in,\n  watch it parse & index live in the browser.\n- Layout: left = upload + file list, middle = doc\n  text + citation map, right = SHA-256 + logs.\n- EXPORT: rebuild a .docx -> open a Gmail draft;\n  toggle theme, font scale & full-graph view.\n\nDev:    npm install && npm run dev\nOpen:   http://localhost:5173",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Built with Vite + React (npm install once).\n- LANDING -> ENTER WORKSPACE / SCAN / EXPORT.\n- SCAN: drag a .docx/.pdf/.md/.txt/.json file in,\n  watch it parse & index live in the browser.\n- Layout: left = upload + file list, middle = doc\n  text + citation map, right = SHA-256 + logs.\n- EXPORT: rebuild a .docx -> open a Gmail draft;\n  toggle theme, font scale & full-graph view.\n\nDev:    npm install && npm run dev\nOpen:   http://localhost:5173",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 13,
      "index": "aB",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r-13",
      "x": 1281.6207170020361,
      "y": 635.1224941463205,
